Get in!

38:09.745 --> 38:12.581
-[alarm continues blaring]
-[clamoring continues]

38:12.665 --> 38:14.542
[automated voice]
Commence shelter protocol.

38:14.625 --> 38:16.002
Return to your homes.

38:16.085 --> 38:17.586
[people shouting]

