38:45.656 --> 38:48.326
Everybody, can I please
get your attention?

38:48.409 --> 38:51.495
Whoever wrote that up there is right.

38:51.579 --> 38:54.040
They are lying to us.

38:55.333 --> 38:56.792
[tires screeching]

38:57.918 --> 39:00.046
-[Sinatra sighs deeply]
-Where are they taking us?

39:00.129 --> 39:01.213
Shelter protocol.

39:01.756 --> 39:04.967
All senior officials and families
are taken to a secure location.

